type: `boolean | null`





### ignoreInlineComments

type: `boolean | null`





### ignorePattern

type: `string | null`





### line

type: `object | null`





#### line.ignoreConsecutiveComments

type: `boolean | null`





#### line.ignoreInlineComments

type: `boolean | null`





#### line.ignorePattern

type: `string | null`








## How to use

To **enable** this rule using the config file or in the CLI, you can use:

